I suggest we use a proper email sending service to send out emails.

Because:
  - This will prevent us from falling into spam folders
  - Greatly simplify sending emails, removes the need for managing SMTP altogether.
  - Will simplify sending emails in bulk later.
  - Allows us a good API interface for testing


We can try resend with fastapi: https://resend.com/docs/send-with-fastapi

Example repo: https://github.com/resend/resend-fastapi-example

Pricing is very low https://resend.com/pricing

We can send 5000 emails per month and 100 a day for $0 a month.
We can send 50,000 emails per month with no daily limit for $20 a month.